full_title: Think U The Shit (Fart) by Ice Spice
title: Think U The Shit (Fart)

description.plain:
On “Think U The Shit (Fart),” Ice Spice compares herself to another woman using comparisons such as the now viral line:

Think you the shit, bitch?
You not even the fart

The first snippet of the song was released on Ice’s socials on January 7, 2024, equipped with a Mario meme with a caption of the chorus' lyrics.
